sts in the world.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eHe assisted in the development of the atomic bomb and was a member of the panel that investigated the Space Shuttle Challenger disaster. In addition to his work in theoretical physics, Feynman has been credited with pioneering the field of quantum computing, and introducing the concept of nanotechnology (creation of devices at the molecular scale). He held the Richard Chace Tolman professorship in theoretical physics at Caltech.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e-wikipedia\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eSee \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/7449671.______________\" title=\"Ричард Фейнман\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eРичард Фейнман\u003c/a\u003e","isGrAuthor":false,"works":{"__typename":"ContributorWorksConnection","totalCount":156},"profileImageUrl":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/authors/1498916887i/1429989._UX200_CR0,41,200,200_.jpg","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/1429989.Richard_P_Feynman","user":null,"viewerIsFollowing":null,"followers":{"__typename":"ContributorFollowersConnection","totalCount":4935}},"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.PZfcB6F7_mOIsO9TUKPDDQ":{"id":"kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.PZfcB6F7_mOIsO9TUKPDDQ","__typename":"Contributor","name":"Микола Климчук","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/6893212._","isGrAuthor":false},"Series:kca://series/amzn1.gr.series.v3.1_OjciZQdUpBGVtt":{"id":"kca://series/amzn1.gr.series.v3.1_OjciZQdUpBGVtt","__typename":"Series","title":"Feynman","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/series/299059-feynman"},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.s-xQrV6yyX_suirVo1ixpg":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.s-xQrV6yyX_suirVo1ixpg","__typename":"Book","legacyId":35167685,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/35167685-surely-you-re-joking-mr-feynman"},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.B5DL6dsfDijNvjmZsjqmsQ":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.B5DL6dsfDijNvjmZsjqmsQ","__typename":"Book"